The paper focuses on expert finding in Community Question Answering (CQA), which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses various machine learning models, including deep learning and ensemble learning, which are relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper also touches upon social network analysis, which falls under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
